NAME
       cmuwmtopbm  - convert a CMU window manager bitmap into a
       PBM image


SYNOPSIS
       cmuwmtopbm [cmuwmfile]


DESCRIPTION
       This program is part of Netpbm(1).

       cmuwmtopbm reads a CMU window manager bitmap  as  input.
       and produces a PBM image as output.
